INCREDIBLE VALUE AT $429,000. PLUS SELLER OFFERS $10,000 CONSESSION FOR CLOSING COSTS OR MORGAGE RATE BUY DOWN.
Exceptional Home, Exceptional Location. Large Cul-de-Sac lot in South Mandarin offers so much. Immaculate Home, new floors throughout, neutral colors, and majestic Oaks highlight this stunning property. Unbeatable award winning schools and Asset Appreciation are ideal for the young family, and retiree alike.
